Description
-----------

The areaportal global keyword makes the associated material function as a [visportal](Visportal "Visportal") .

Usage
-----

In the global section of your material shader type...

    areaportal

Parameters
----------

None.

Notes
-----

As there is already a visportal texture available, level designers should never need to use this option in their own materials.

